  "detailed_description": "Pixel Puzzles 4k: Japan combines a traditional jigsaw puzzle style gameplay with light video-game interactivity. Build puzzles and attain a higher state of consciousness. All hand drawn in a beautiful Japanese aesthetic, Pixel Puzzles: Japan is perfect for puzzlers and gamers alike.<h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >Features:</h2><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li>Traditional puzzle gameplay.<br></li><li>Relaxing Japanese atmosphere.<br></li><li>25 puzzles in a range of sizes from 84 to 432 pieces.<br></li><li>Beautiful 4k photos taken on site in Japan.<br></li><li>Interactive play environment.</li></ul>",
